content: 'Destiny Chen joined the Department of Computer Science as a Project Administrator in December 2012. She supports a portfolio of six research projects under the Quantum Group through:

Label: I

content: 'Destiny has had significant experience in Higher Education administration from working in five different departments at both Oxford Brookes University and the University of Oxford, in areas including staff development activities, marketing, events, course administration and student support, PA, and international collaborative projects.
Label: I

content: 'Destiny holds a BA TEFL, Distinction (Guangzhou University, China) and an MA in Educational Studies, Merit (Oxford Brookes University, England).
Label: I

content: 'Outside work Destiny enjoys cycling, yoga, good books and music, gardening and all styles of dancing.
